## SCAFFOLD 
Comando per aggiornamento delle Tabelle del Database

Scaffold-DbContext 'Server=127.0.0.1;User ID=root;Password='password';Database=pizza' MySql.EntityFrameworkCore -OutputDir ../ModelDto/Models -Context MyContext -Namespace ModelDto.Models -NoOnConfiguring -f

## CREATES MIGRATION

 Add-Migration <Name>  -Context MyContext  -OutputDir ../ModelDto/Migrations/MariaDB

## Comando di compilazione

dotnet publish -o  C:\\inetpub\\sites\\pizzeria /p:EnvironmentName=Development  /p:Configuration=Release /p:RestorePackagesConfig=true /p:EnableMSDeployAppOffline=true /p:MSDeployUseChecksum=true